{"tid":2374358,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警察涉勾結黑幫案一再押後 警複製卧底三部手機 發現兩部壞機","createTime":"2021-01-21T07:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T07:52:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7fade96b8606051f455086c6ab25b097aa95b998","tid":2374358,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"荃灣反黑組四名警員疑串謀黑幫策劃「假掃蕩」，遭滲入黑幫的O記卧底踢爆，被控串謀妨礙司法公正罪。案件審至第五天，控辯雙方除繼續爭議是否披露臥底警開銷記錄外，案件再添枝節；控方早前承諾披露臥底所使用的三部手提電話內容，惟今早突然透露，警方在複製內容期間發現其中兩部電話損壞。辯方表明要找專家檢驗損壞電話，法庭再次押後案件。<br />\n<br />\n案件今早在區域法院續審，四名警員包括趙廣林、賴福康、傅裕文、張子健（年齡介乎28至54歲）被控於2018年5月2日至7月10日期間，串謀賭場負責人陳少寶、和勝和其中一個派系「阿頂」綽號「菜仔」的王偉軍，以及一名叫「Eddy」的人士犯案。陳少寶早前認罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/3S4ONJPZD5AM5N32YANE5UXOAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2F3S4ONJPZD5AM5N32YANE5UXOAU%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcIXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=b9184507\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2F3S4ONJPZD5AM5N32YANE5UXOAU%2F&h=2d2248bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/3S4ONJPZD5AM5N32YANE5UXOAU/</a>"},{"pid":"ba0736e8aeb3b7a7544d2d31d825e4b4cfafca55","tid":2374358,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"控方早前承諾披露臥底所使用的三部手提電話內容，惟今早突然透露，警方在複製電話內容期間發現其中兩部電話損壞。勞官聞言問：「其實呢啲未解決，件案都開唔到喇？」辯方同意，並指內容對辯方盤問證人很重要。<br />\n<br />\n勞官質疑：「呢啲take完plea (答辯完) 就同我講喇，咁重要嘅問題！」辯方回應指控方早已承諾披露，「唔知cloning（複製），clone clone吓會壞咗。」惟勞官即謂雖然控方承諾披露，問辯方「咁你開唔開唔到呀」，尤其有關資料對盤問證人有關，強調：「咁重要嘅嘢要解決咗先開庭，要第一時間解決呀！」<br />\n<br />\n辯方其後表示，由於不知道兩部電話何時損壞及為何損壞，考慮傳召專家檢驗兩部電話。控方最終安排辯方今午到灣仔警察總部，在警方專家陪同下初步檢驗兩部損壞的電話，以及檢視餘下一部運作良好的電話。"},{"pid":"c97e4f11ce0866f822c8f0ea97eeb64829a794a7","tid":2374358,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8f9ce63bb0846cdd73ccf2cb9868677e67af87","tid":2374358,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"球證都係我嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c42828aa4d0ced3028953052700e0387ce53e4","tid":2374358,"uid":73565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:25:32.000Z","msg":"一場誤會 退堂"},{"pid":"369af2a1bb56aba597c0b04f980ffa319ca7300b","tid":2374358,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"都話左我地警察係唔洗守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100cd05df0705232311e50ffc60af586e5c41a1f","tid":2374358,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分贓不均？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02920c2635247c94b371ca37068f2da1c3cc05c","tid":2374358,"uid":289214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"訓斥下算啦"},{"pid":"325e3498c407a17a1ef802c0d24201bc67c36789","tid":2374358,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"同場加映動物生態紀錄片"},{"pid":"bb273fc8d9bd422c2fcb9d285652fc272508e673","tid":2374358,"uid":218731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"派去黑社會嘅臥底其實係黑社會派去嘅臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00483e4be858ba94bfb9c1404fe77efbad0dad52","tid":2374358,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"即係冇證據, 放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1d1f7d1